[Since the initial introduction of the virus from Georgia in November 2007, 263 outbreaks in domestic and wild swine have been reported from the Russian Federation, throughout vast parts of European Russia from south to north; see interactive OIE map (zoom in!) showing the accumulated outbreaks as of 30 Jul 2012 (not yet including the current outbreak in Krasnodar), at http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=8462. - Mod.AS

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1z-D.]
